sun valley serenade is a 1941 musical film starring sonja &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; , john payne , glenn miller , milton berle , and lynn bari . it features the glenn miller orchestra as well as dancing by the nicholas brothers and dorothy dandridge , performing " chattanooga choo choo " , which was nominated for an academy award for best song , was inducted into the grammy hall of fame in 1996 , and was awarded the first gold record for sales of 1.2 million .